  "description": "<p>\n\t<img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201305/ca59b3e726274f518deae8f099b9af1a.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; margin-left: 5px; border-top: 0px; margin-right: 5px; border-right: 0px;\" /></p>\n<p>\n\t《英文天天写》是沪江部落一档写作类节目，其目的在于提升大家的英语写作能力。每期节目主持人都会给出一个话题，积极参加的童鞋还会得到主持人的专业点评哦！想提高英语写作的童鞋千万不要错过哦！<a href=\"http://pass.hujiang.com/signup/?source=en_sqyd&amp;url=http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/\" style=\"color: rgb(0,90,148); text-decoration: none;\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"http://i2.w.yun.hjfile.cn/doc/201304/d5e293c817a6488d819f0c13a95230e1.jpg\" style=\"border-bottom: 0px; border-left: 0px; line-height: 1.8em; margin-left: 5px; border-top: 0px; margin-right: 5px; border-right: 0px;\" /></a>去沪江部落订阅本节目！</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>背景介绍：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tCreativity expert Sir Ken Robinson challenges the way we're educating our children. He champions a radical rethink of our school systems, to cultivate creativity and acknowledge multiple types of intelligence.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>话题：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tYour opinions after watching the video above.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例1：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\t&quot;'Gao Kao' is no longer able to determine your entire life&quot;, this is a nongovernmental <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/interpretation\" target=\"_blank\">interpretation</a> of the recent significant decisions on education reform made by our party leaders. Regardless of its possibility of realization, again it stirs a <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/whirlpool\" target=\"_blank\">whirlpool</a> of emotion in thousands of minds. At the TED Talks Education, Sir Ken Robinson embraced an <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/elaborate\" target=\"_blank\">elaborate</a> <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/metaphor\" target=\"_blank\">metaphor</a> where the current global education is like a &quot;Death Valley&quot;, which, however, is not dead but <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/dormant\" target=\"_blank\">dormant</a>, where policy makers, instead of bringing in the demand and control, should embrace the climate control. To the most parts of our current education system, the opinions of Sir Ken Robinson is surely of value.<br />\n\tEducation plays an irreplaceable role in the efforts of eliminating social problems provoked by the wider and wider wealth gap. Sush is human nature, that jealousness, dissatisfaction and even <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/irrational\" target=\"_blank\">irrational</a> hatred grows when civilians are constantly <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/haunted\" target=\"_blank\">haunted</a> by the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/strut\" target=\"_blank\">strut</a> of some super rich and vested interest groups. However, it is the equal access to education of high quality, that gives everyone the skills they need to get the opportunity, that assures them of the opportunity to realize their dreams. Great leaders know this, and that is one of the reasons for the rise of prosperous countries throughout the history.<br />\n\tAs a student passing by, I am not completely confident about the instant recovery of our education system, but I do hope that those students incoming-maybe your and my children-can see a world with more color during their childhood.</p>\n<p>\n\t<strong>范例2：</strong></p>\n<p>\n\tThroughout history, teachers have always been standing in a high position for playing an important role in teaching knowledge and leading them in the right direction mentally. However, teachers nowadays seem to be trapped in the <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/mire\" target=\"_blank\">mire</a> of pursuing reputation. They tend to <a class=\"hjdict\" href=\"http://dict.hjenglish.com/w/unilaterally\" target=\"_blank\">unilaterally</a> give lessons to prove their high standards while neglecting students&rsquo; abilities to turn the knowledge into their own, let alone students will have their own understanding. The current education climate is mainly focused on getting a high score, which is inconformity with an old saying that give a man a fish and you will feed him for a day; teach him how to fish and you will feed him for a lifetime. It is actually essential for teachers to create a favorable study climate for students so that they are able to accept knowledge voluntarily, exerting their own creation. That&rsquo;s why the education reform has underway recently in our country.</p>\n<p>\n\t想要得到专业主持人的点评和意见吗？<a href=\"http://bulo.hujiang.com/menu/15011/item/852308/\" target=\"_blank\">快来节目现场一试身手吧&gt;&gt;</a><br />\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<br /><center><a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p573504/#relate_articles\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_chat.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a> <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/new/p573504\"><img src=\"http://en.hujiang.com/2009/images/rss_digg.jpg\" style=\"border: 0;\" /></a></center><h3 style=\"margin: 10px;\">本周最热文章</h3><ul style=\"margin: 5px 0;\"><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p566816/\">善待大脑:让大脑更锋利的5个健脑技巧</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p571122/\">2013全球百大英俊男士 你的男神上榜了吗？</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p570754/\">猫奴主人看过来：喵星人是这样看你的！</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p571244/\">大家的分享：15条永不过时的生活智慧</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p103560/\">沪江英语资料下载帮助及沪元知识</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p575341/\">17岁辍学创业者发明新型计算机</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p574960/\">奥巴马总统2014年国情咨文（双语对照）</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p554974/\">英雄不问出身：亿万富翁的首份工作</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p568864/\">春节观影指南：奥斯卡热门提名逐一看</a></li><li style=\"margin: 2px 0 2px 20px;\"><a href=\"http://en.hujiang.com/new/p564743/\">专业升职术：这样奋斗才有意义</a></li></ul><div style=\"margin-top: 10px;\">导航:  <a href=\"http://www.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江网</a>  <a href=\"http://www.hjenglish.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江英语</a>  <a href=\"http://jp.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江日语</a>  <a href=\"http://fr.hujiang.com/\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江法语</a>  <a href=\"http://kr.hujiang.com\" style=\"margin: 5px;\" target=\"_black\">沪江韩语</a></div><hr style=\"border: 0.5px solid gray;\" />", 
